data.description: FARMHOUSE CHARM! Come take a look at this gorgeous three bedroom, two bath ranch-style home situated on 15.006-acres, in a perfect location just outside of town. Nestled among towering oaks, this home offers great views from its large covered front and back porches. Whether entertaining guests around the firepit or at 40’x30’ insulated barn, both make for a fun hangout spot year-round. If you have few horses or cows, then the stock tank and covered stall will be an additional incentive that comes with this property. There is no shortage of covered parking for multiple vehicles under the detached carport with concrete flooring or with the covered RV parking attached to the barn. Upon entering the home, you’ll appreciate the numerous updates done in every room, including the large farmhouse sink, freshly painted shiplap, and double French doors leading to the backyard. All the bedrooms have gorgeous tile and lighting. The primary bedroom has private bath with a shower/tub combo, while the guest bedrooms share a  hall bath with a  large walk-in tile shower. If this sounds like the home you’ve been looking for then give us a call to schedule a private tour!
